com.betfair.cougar.client

Class CougarRequestFactory<HR>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betfair.cougar.client.CougarRequestFactory<HR>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    HttpClientCougarRequestFactory

    public abstract class CougarRequestFactory<HR>
extends Object
    CougarRequestFactory describes contract and base behaviour for creating http requests on client side. Particular implementations are to be used within each actual transport.
